tagDescription: Indian Affairs, Peigan Reserve - memoranda Concerning the Peigan Reserve of the North West Territories.
Indian Affairs - report on Setting Bull's arrival to Canada, ca. 1880, and a report on Department if Indian Affairs officials in the North West Territories , 1897.
Shipbuilding - memorial to federal government to aid ship building in Canada.
Hudson's Bay Company - memorandum Concerning the grants of land to the Company by the Order - in - Council of 5 July 1869.
Manitoba - memoranda Concerning a land investment in Dauphin and Concerning the Manitoba School Question.
Elections - clippings from the Winnipeg Daily Tribune and reports from an informant identified as #138 Concerning the state of public during the 1908 General election.
North West Mounted Police - personnel file.
Patronage List - list of recipients in Manitoba and the North West Territories.
North West Territories - General services account.
Grain trade - memorandum on the Act to regulate the grain trade in Manitoba and the North West Territories.
Stoney Mountain Penitentiary - investigation of conditions.
Railways - memoranda regarding forest fires in railway right - of - ways.
